text: Gabriella Izzo (born August 5, 2001) is an American figure skater. She is the 2019 CS Asian Open Trophy bronze medalist and the 2019 Egna Spring Trophy champion. On the junior level, she is the 2018 Asian Open Trophy silver medalist, and the 2019 U.S. junior national champion. == Programs == {|class=wikitable style=text-align:center ! Season ! Short program !
